<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes primarily disturb stands rather than fire. <i>Salix lucida </i>is top-killed by low- and moderate-intensity fire, though plants may sprout vigorously.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
			<td class="key">Fire return interval</td>
